{{!-- create、edit 可以共用的原因是：hbs 若看到花瓜裡面的內容變數不存在不會噴錯，會直接忽略 --}}
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="name">Name</label>
  <input class="form-control" type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="Enter name" required value="{{ restaurant.name }}">
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label for="categoryId">Category</label>
  <select name="categoryId" id="categoryId" class="form-control">
    {{#each categories}}
    <option value="{{ this.id }}" {{#ifCond this.id ../restaurant.categoryId}}selected{{/ifCond}}>{{ this.name }}
    </option>
    {{/each}}
    {{!-- this.id(A) restaurant.categoryId(B)，這邊使用../是因為 context(語境)問題，用 ../ 回到上一層語境才能取得 restaurant.CategoryId，若沒有使用 ../
    hbs 會以為在呼叫 this.restaurant，使 B 變成 restaurant --}}
  </select>
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="tel">Tel</label>
  <input class="form-control" type="text" name="tel" id="tel" placeholder="Enter tel" value="{{ restaurant.tel }}">
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="address">Address</label>
  <input class="form-control" type="text" name="address" id="address" placeholder="Enter address"
    value="{{ restaurant.address }}">
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="openingHours">Opening Hours</label>
  <input class="form-control" type="time" name="openingHours" id="openingHours" placeholder="Enter opening hours"
    value="{{ restaurant.openingHours }}">
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="description">Description</label>
  <textarea class="form-control" id="description" name="description" rows="3">{{ restaurant.description }}</textarea>
</div>
<div class="form-row mb-3">
  <label class="form-label" for="image">Image</label>
  <input class="form-control" type="file" class="form-control-file" id="image" name="image">
</div>
<a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="javascript:history.back()" onclick="return confirm('目前編輯資料將會消失'
)">Back</a>
<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>